snippet.title: Towers Inc Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1337640/Towers_Inc/

Build and manage your own corporate tower in this minimalist take on the tower building genre. Satisfy the needs of renters and keep them happy by adding services and utilities while balancing finances. Build and manage your tower the way you want to.
